parameters.name: MET
parameters.description: Mission elapsed time for the last burst record in the burst observation.

parameters.name: DELTA_T
parameters.description: An offset time from the MET for the last burst record in the burst observation. Provides 50 msec resolution to the time stamp for the last burst record.

parameters.name: NUM_BURST_PKTS
parameters.description: Number of burst packets downloaded for the burst observation. Nominally there should be 15 burst packets for one complete burst observation. A value of less than 15 indicates missing packets.

parameters.name: ACTUAL_RANGE
parameters.description: Actual range used by MAG. =0 2048 nT, =1 65536 nT
